{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:5YEOFR10PoseTargetO12yawThresholdSdvpZ","modules":[{"name":"YEOFR"}],"title":"yawThreshold","roleHeading":"Type Property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"yawThreshold"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","text":"Double"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/PoseTarget\/yawThreshold","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/PoseTarget"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"yawThreshold"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","text":"Double"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Narrowed in stages (±15° → ±10° → ±8° → ±7°): users reported having"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to “turn a lot” before a turn pose accepted. Vision’s yaw estimate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"compresses the physical rotation (the same effect documented for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pitch below, milder on yaw), and at large physical turns Vision"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"often drops yaw to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" — which disables the blind-Vision time"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fallback (a readable angle was seen earlier in the pose), so the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pose can only clear via the ~10 s stall cap. Opening the matched"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"window at ±7° lets the hold accumulate at a smaller, more reliably"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"readable angle. Still clears the ±5° "},{"code":"front","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" zone with a 2° margin."}]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"±7° in radians — the yaw turn-pose gate ("},{"code":"yawLeft","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" \/ "},{"code":"yawRight","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/posetarget\/yawthreshold"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/PoseTarget":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Target head orientation for one slot of a gallery enrollment."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PoseTarget","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PoseTarget"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/PoseTarget","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/posetarget","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PoseTarget"}]},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/PoseTarget/yawThreshold":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"±7° in radians — the yaw turn-pose gate ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"yawLeft"},{"type":"text","text":" \/ "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"yawRight"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"yawThreshold","fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"yawThreshold","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text"